    </em>
    </h4>
    
    by 
	<a href="/node/578">AQ Online</a>	
    <br>
    <div style="width:100px;padding-top:5px;float:left;margin-right:8px;">
        <a class="imagefield imagefield-nodelink imagefield-field_thumbnail" href="/content/aq-video-entrevista-con-sergio-dahbar">
            <div class="field field-name-field-thumbnail field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/content/aq-video-entrevista-con-sergio-dahbar"><img src="http://www.americasquarterly.org/sites/default/files/Freedom%20of%20expression%20100x100_0.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="" /></a></div></div></div>        </a>
