    <div style="width:200px;padding-top:5px;float:left;">
        <div class="field field-name-field-dek field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">El periodista venezolano Sergio Dahbar habla con Americas Quarterly sobre el clima para hacer periodismo en Venezuela hoy.</div></div></div>    </div>
    <div style="clear:both;"></div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-2 views-row-even views-row-last">    <div class="onlineFeaturesTitle">
        <a href="/content/incumbents-arent-latin-americas-problem">Incumbents Aren’t Latin America’s Problem</a>    </div>
    <h4 class="onlineFeaturesDate">
    <em>
        <span class="date-display-single"><div class="field field-name-field-date field-type-date field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><span class="date-display-single">November 6, 2014</span></div></div></div></span>
    </em>
    </h4>
    
    by 
	<a href="/content/kevin-lees">Kevin Lees</a>	
    <br>
    <div style="width:100px;padding-top:5px;float:left;margin-right:8px;">
        <a class="imagefield imagefield-nodelink imagefield-field_thumbnail" href="/content/incumbents-arent-latin-americas-problem">
            <div class="field field-name-field-thumbnail field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/content/incumbents-arent-latin-americas-problem"><img src="http://www.americasquarterly.org/sites/default/files/11333263144_ea926f1bb3_q.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="" /></a></div></div></div>        </a>
    </div>
    <div style="width:200px;padding-top:5px;float:left;">
        <div class="field field-name-field-dek field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">It’s been an exceptionally good year for incumbents in Latin America.</div></div></div>    </div>
    <div style="clear:both;"></div></li>
